- Reports ([Reports.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Anis/Documents/Web%20Pages/Fleet%20project/fleet-management-app/frontend/src/pages/Reports.tsx))
- Alert Rules ([AlertRules.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Anis/Documents/Web%20Pages/Fleet%20project/fleet-management-app/frontend/src/pages/AlertRules.tsx))
- Users ([Users.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Anis/Documents/Web%20Pages/Fleet%20project/fleet-management-app/frontend/src/pages/Users.tsx), [UserForm.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Anis/Documents/Web%20Pages/Fleet%20project/fleet-management-app/frontend/src/pages/UserForm.tsx))

